{"prompt": "Design an engaging platform for a virtual reality development studio. The aesthetic should incorporate a vibrant electric blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Quantum Realities - VR Development Studio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 60px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 80px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #007bff;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #007bff;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        .features, .services {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n        .feature-item, .service-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-top: 5px solid #007bff;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover, .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3, .service-item h3 {\n            color: #007bff;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .feature-item p, .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0056b3 0%, #007bff 100%);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #fff;\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #007bff;\n            padding: 15px 35px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: #fff;\n            border-color: #fff;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #222;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #007bff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .orb {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,123,255,0.3) 0%, rgba(0,123,255,0) 70%);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            filter: blur(50px);\n            animation: pulse 4s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .orb.top-left { top: 50px; left: 50px; }\n        .orb.bottom-right { bottom: 50px; right: 50px; animation-delay: 2s; }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.5; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8em; }\n            .hero p { font-size: 1em; }\n            .section h2 { font-size: 2em; }\n            .container { padding: 0 15px; }\n            .features, .services { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n            .cta h2 { font-size: 2em; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"orb top-left\"></div>\n        <div class=\"orb bottom-right\"></div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Quantum Realities</h1>\n            <p>Crafting immersive virtual experiences that redefine interaction and imagination.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Our Vision</h2>\n            <p>At Quantum Realities, we are pioneers in the virtual realm. We blend cutting-edge technology with artistic vision to create VR experiences that are not just seen, but felt. From breathtaking game worlds to revolutionary training simulations, we build the future of immersion.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>What We Do</h2>\n            <div class=\"services\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>VR Game Development</h3>\n                    <p>Immerse players in captivating narratives and groundbreaking gameplay mechanics that push the boundaries of virtual entertainment.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Interactive Simulations</h3>\n                    <p>Develop realistic and engaging VR training, educational, and architectural visualization tools for enhanced learning and design.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Custom VR Solutions</h3>\n                    <p>Collaborate with you to bring your unique ideas to life, creating bespoke VR applications tailored to your specific needs.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Our Process</h2>\n            <div class=\"features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Ideation & Concept</h3>\n                    <p>We begin by deeply understanding your goals and vision to lay a strong foundation for the virtual world.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Design & Prototyping</h3>\n                    <p>Our team crafts intuitive interfaces and compelling environments, bringing concepts to life through rapid prototyping.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Development & Optimization</h3>\n                    <p>Leveraging the latest VR technologies, we build and refine experiences for seamless performance and maximum impact.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Testing & Deployment</h3>\n                    <p>Rigorous testing ensures a polished and bug-free experience, ready for your audience to explore.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"cta\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2>Ready to Explore the Impossible?</h2>\n                <p>Let's build your next virtual reality masterpiece together.</p>\n                <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Get In Touch</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Quantum Realities. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@quantumrealities.com\">info@quantumrealities.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic animation for orbs\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const orbs = document.querySelectorAll('.orb');\n            orbs.forEach((orb, index) => {\n                const delay = index * 2; // Stagger animation start\n                orb.style.animationDelay = `${delay}s`;\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}